FBIS4-15448 "drsov068_v_94012" FBIS-SOV-94-068 Daily Report 7 Apr 1994 Lithuania Social Democrats Lack Confidence in Government Social Democrats Lack Confidence in Government LD0704100894 Vilnius Radio Vilnius Network in Lithuanian 0900 GMT 7 Apr 94 LD0704100894 Vilnius Radio Vilnius Network Lithuanian BFN [Text] The faction of Lithuanian social democrats, fulfilling its promise, on 5-6 April officially submitted to other factions of the Lithuanian Seimas its motives of no confidence in the work of the Lithuanian Democratic Labor Party government, led by Adolfas Slezevicius, and a draft statement of no confidence in the government.
